Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[BTV-4 has been recently reported to spread in several other south European countries, including:

1. Montenegro, where it reportedly started 11 Aug 2016, 59 (submitted) outbreaks reported so far:
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Sheep / 2109 / 286 / 61 / 99 / 0
Cattle / 23 / 6 / 0 / 0 / 0
Sheep & goats / 198 / 22 / 6 / 6 / 0
Goats / 40 / 1 / 0 / 0 / 0

2. Italy, where it reportedly started 28 Aug 2016, 60 (submitted) outbreaks reported so far:
