Sheep / 3739 / 51 / 5 / 0 / 0
Cattle / 653 / 78 / 0 / 0 / 0
Mouflon / - / 1 / 1 / - / -
Goats / 210 / 5 / 0 / 0 / 0

3. Croatia, where it reportedly started 21 Sep 2016, 3 (submitted) outbreaks reported so far:
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Sheep / 154 / 4 / 0 / 0 / 0
Cattle / 8 / 0 / 0 / 0 / 0
Goats / 157 / 0 / 0 / 0 / 0

An outbreak in Bosnia and Herzegovina, which reportedly started 19 Aug 2016, has not yet been serotyped (or serotype not published). - Mods.AS/CRD

